#comment: Saucy Changes: Moved to FNAF Gorblin lawn. Each grave number now comes with a gorblin question, with the gorblins spawning on the following wave. Gorblins act like almost invincible ghosts (other gorblin types can also spawn later). Removed '0' graves. Increased starting sun. Try to survive with as few gorblin counters as possible! | Maw waz here

objdata.Description:
Solve the gorblin's riddles!
Hint: Riddles can be answered anywhere along the lane, gorblins are indestructible
Bonus Objective: Use as few gorblin-destroying plants as you can

objdata.WaveStartMessage:
Welcome to the pre-test! Please use the complimentary test sheet for all the questions.

Where is the arrow pointing?
How many unique Ultraviolet and Hot Sauce challenges have been launched prior to this one?
How many nights were spent in this pizzeria in Five Nights at Freddy's 1?
I dropped my nose! Can you help me?
Do the gravestones show a number that is on my lawn?
Lastly, did you answer these questions without cheating for the answers?
